      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Telechargements (ComfyUI-Shared/models)\n\n**UNET** `diffusion_models/`\n- fp8 (~12 Go, 5080 serre): https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/flux1-kontext-dev_ComfyUI/resolve/main/split_files/diffusion_models/flux1-dev-kontext_fp8_scaled.safetensors\n\n**Text encoders** `text_encoders/`\n- clip_l: https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors\n- t5xxl_fp16 (recommande): https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp16.safetensors\n\n**VAE** `vae/`\n- ae.safetensors: https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/Lumina_Image_2.0_Repackaged/resolve/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors\n\n**H100** : meme UNET fp8 OK si t5xxl_fp16. Pour bf16 natif voir repo BFL FLUX.1-Kontext-dev (~24 Go).\n\nTutoriel: https://docs.comfy.org/tutorials/flux/flux-1-kontext-dev"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "LIENS MODELES COMPLETS"
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "type": "MarkdownNote",
      "pos": [200, 920],
      "size": [680, 280],
      "flags": {},
      "order": 31,
      "mode": 0,
      "inputs": [],
      "outputs": [],
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Iteration — pourquoi ca bloquait\n\nCe workflow enchaine **PASS 1 → PASS 2 en 1 seule queue** (pas recharger a la main).\n\n- PASS 1 : 1 changement (ex: corps)\n- PASS 2 : **uniquement** le 2e changement (ex: veste) — ne redis pas le pass 1\n- Chaque sampler a sa propre seed randomize\n- DualCLIP type = **flux** (si SDXL → image cassee / prompt ignore)\n- Verifie pass1/ et pass2/ dans output avant le polish ZiT\n- Mute le noeud ZiT pour tester Kontext seul\n\nPASS 3 : duplique le bloc PASS 2 ou relance avec LoadImageOutput depuis pass2/"
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653",
      "title": "Mode d'emploi"
    }
  ],
